<http://dx.doi.org/10.3897/zookeys.1059.68140.figure6>
    dc:description "Figure 6. Morphological features of the adult male holotype NHMG 202007003 of Nidirana guangxiensis sp. nov. in preservative A dorsal view B ventral view C lateral view D right hand E right foot. Photos by Shuo Qi." ;
    fabio:hasRepresentation "https://binary.pensoft.net/fig/584223" ;
    a fabio:Figure .

<http://dx.doi.org/10.3897/zookeys.1059.68140.figure7>
    dc:description "Figure 7. Variation and colorations of Nidirana guangxiensis sp. nov. in life A, B male holotype NHMG 202007003 C female paratype NHMG 202007001 D male paratype NHMG 202007002 E, F uncaptured female and male individuals in the wild. Photos by Zhong Huang, Zhi-Tong Lyu, and Yun-Ming Mo." ;
    fabio:hasRepresentation "https://binary.pensoft.net/fig/584224" ;
    a fabio:Figure .

<http://dx.doi.org/10.3897/zookeys.1059.68140.figure8>
    dc:description "Figure 8. Tadpole SYS a 008814 of Nidirana guangxiensis sp. nov. Photos by Shuo Qi." ;
    fabio:hasRepresentation "https://binary.pensoft.net/fig/584225" ;
    a fabio:Figure .

<http://dx.doi.org/10.3897/zookeys.1059.68140.figure1>
    dc:description "Figure 1. Map showing the collected localities for the Nidirana samples of Clade C (see Fig. 2) used in this study." ;
    fabio:hasRepresentation "https://binary.pensoft.net/fig/584218" ;
    a fabio:Figure .

<http://dx.doi.org/10.3897/zookeys.1059.68140.figure9>
    dc:description "Figure 9. A habitat of Nidirana guangxiensis sp. nov. in the type locality in Mt Daming B a male calling in a nest and two nests filled with half of water. Photos by Yun-Ming Mo and Shuo Qi." ;
    fabio:hasRepresentation "https://binary.pensoft.net/fig/584226" ;
    a fabio:Figure .

